# Custom Lighting System — Implementation Plan

## Context

CineBlock's StudioView has hardcoded `ambientLight` (0.5) and `directionalLight` (1.0) with no user control. This plan adds a full custom lighting system: placeable point/spot lights with temperature, tint, intensity, and range controls — plus master sliders for the existing scene lights. Lights are per-shot with copy-on-switch, togglable via a toolbar button, and their helper visuals are hidden during captures.

